This is a mail forwarder Yii Framework extension.

Dependency

* PHPMailer


Yii config main.php exapmle:

`
	'components'=>array(
		'Smtpmail'=>array(
			'class'=>'application.extensions.mailer.mailer',
			'URL'=>'http://name.or.ip.to.your.forwarder.server/path/to/mailer/forwarder.php',
			'System'=>'<The subject prefix made by forwarder>',
		),
	)
`
